在[[粒子物理学|粒子物理学]][[标准模型|标准模型]]的[[超对称|超对称]]扩展中，'''超费米子'''是一种假想的[[超对称|超对称]]费米子，[[自旋|自旋]]为0。<ref>{{cite book |last1=He-sheng |first1=Chen |last2=Dongsheng |first2=Du |last3=Weiguo |first3=Li |title=High Energy Physics: Ichep 2004 - Proceedings Of The 32nd International Conference (In 2 Volumes) |date=2005 |publisher=World Scientific |isbn=9789814481274 |page=109 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=W7DKCgAAQBAJ&q=Sfermion+spin-0&pg=PA109 |access-date=30 September 2019 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Masayuki |first1=Nakahata |last2=Y |first2=Itow |last3=Masato |first3=Shiozawa |title=Neutrino Oscillations And Their Origin, Proceedings Of The 4th International Workshop |date=2004 |publisher=World Scientific |isbn=9789814485586 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GhzJCgAAQBAJ&q=Sfermion&pg=PA419 |access-date=30 September 2019 |language=en}}</ref>每种粒子都有[[超对称粒子|超对称粒子]]，自旋与其相差{{sfrac|1|2}}。费米子有[[自旋-1/2|自旋-{{sfrac]]，所以它们的超费米子的自旋为0。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Baer |first1=Howard |last2=Tata |first2=Xerxes |title=Weak Scale Supersymmetry: From Superfields to Scattering Events |date=2006 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |isbn=9781139455077 |page=129 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QpwM_3PA2KAC&q=Sfermion+spin-0&pg=PA129 |access-date=30 September 2019 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Cline |first1=David B |title=Flavor-changing Neutral Currents: Present And Future Studies: Proceedings Of The Symposium |date=1997 |publisher=World Scientific |isbn=9789814545822 |page=229 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Go84DwAAQBAJ&q=Sfermion+spin-0&pg=PA229 |access-date=30 September 2019 |language=en}}</ref>

